snippet.title: Story of Amber who was kidnapped in childhood
snippet.description:
Waledain ko aware krny k liye or amber ki help krny k liye ye video share kr ri hun.
Society me kidnapping k wakiat hona aam bat hy.
Leki in kidnappings se jo asrat un khandano pr muratab hoty hen wo bht dil dehla deny waly hoty hen.
Kuch had tak ese wakiat ki rok tham ho

 sakay is liye ye video share kr ri hun.
